summary.span: 为 上存在的任何依赖属性的本地值提供枚举支持。

span.span: Provides enumeration support for the local values of any dependency properties that exist on a .

remarks.format: ## Remarks *本地值*是依赖属性的值, 该属性通过调用, 或更常见地通过使用在内部调用的[!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_clr](~/includes/tla2sharptla-clr-md.md)]属性包装的 set 访问器来设置依赖属性。A *local value* is a value for a dependency property that was set directly on a dependency property, by calling , or more typically by using the set accessor of a [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_clr](~/includes/tla2sharptla-clr-md.md)] property wrapper that calls internally. 其他不是本地值的属性系统 qps 的示例是通过样式或依赖属性默认值设置的值。Examples of other property system determinants that are not local values are values set through styles, or dependency property default values. 有关详细信息，请参阅[依赖属性值优先级](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/dependency-property-value-precedence.md)。For details, see [Dependency Property Value Precedence](~/docs/framework/wpf/advanced/dependency-property-value-precedence.md). 由方法返回, 并实现接口。 A is returned by the method and implements the interface. 公共构造函数不存在; 因此, 必须调用才能获取此类的实例。A public constructor does not exist; therefore, you must call to obtain an instance of this class. 枚举本地值时, 不要修改本地值(通过调用或)。Do not modify local values (by calling or ) while enumerating local values. 如果基于枚举器返回的属性更改或清除属性值, 则更改或清除操作不会使枚举器集合失效, 因为许多实现情况都是如此。If you change or clear the property values based on properties that are returned by the enumerator, the change or clear operations do not invalidate the enumerator collection, as is the case for many implementations. 此外, 枚举器视图也是一个快照。Also, the enumerator view is a snapshot. 不能保证对集合的更改是线程安全的, 并且不会强制实施锁。A change to the collection is not guaranteed to be thread safe, and no lock is enforced. 其他线程仍可以从枚举数以外的上下文中免费访问本地值。Other threads still have free access to the local values from a context other than the enumerator. 如果你在类中具有一些操作, 需要知道某个属性的值是否来自本地值, 请使用此类型。Use this type if you have operations in your class where it is important to know whether a property's value came from a local value. 例如, 在实现中使用此类型, 或在要查询所有本地设置属性的元数据的位置使用此类型。For example, use this type in an implementation, or where you want to query the metadata on all locally set properties.
